=================================================
RH ENTERPRISE - ADVANCED SMART CATEGORY LOGIC
=================================================

PURPOSE:
--------
Category page dynamically decide karega ki:

• Subcategories dikhani hain ya nahi
• Products dikhane hain ya nahi
• Single product ho toh direct redirect karna hai
• Empty state handle karna hai

System fully dynamic hai.
Unlimited category nesting supported hai.

-------------------------------------------------
CORE PRINCIPLE
-------------------------------------------------

Category ke andar 3 cheezein possible hain:

1) Subcategories ho sakti hain
2) Products ho sakte hain
3) Dono ho sakte hain
4) Dono na bhi ho sakte hain

System in sab scenarios ko intelligently handle karta hai.

-------------------------------------------------
UPDATED DECISION FLOW (CURRENT IMPLEMENTATION)
-------------------------------------------------

STEP 1:
Validate category using slug

IF category not found:
    Stop execution (Invalid category)

STEP 2:
Fetch subcategories (status=1)

STEP 3:
Fetch products (status=1)

STEP 4:
SMART REDIRECT CONDITION

IF:
    subcategory_count == 0
    AND product_count == 1

THEN:
    Redirect directly to product page

Why?
Avoid extra click for single product categories.

STEP 5:
DISPLAY LOGIC

IF subcategories exist:
    Show subcategory grid

IF products exist:
    Show product listing grid

IF both exist:
    Show subcategories first
    Then show products below

IF none exist:
    Show empty message

-------------------------------------------------
PSEUDO CODE (FINAL VERSION)
-------------------------------------------------

validate_category()

sub_count = get_subcategory_count()
prod_count = get_product_count()

IF sub_count == 0 AND prod_count == 1:
    redirect_to_product()

IF sub_count > 0:
    show_subcategories()

IF prod_count > 0:
    show_products()

IF sub_count == 0 AND prod_count == 0:
    show_empty_message()

-------------------------------------------------
