-------------------------------------------------
FLOW BEHAVIOUR EXAMPLES
-------------------------------------------------

CASE 1:
Category has subcategories only
→ Show subcategories

CASE 2:
Category has products only
    If 1 product → redirect
    If multiple → show listing

CASE 3:
Category has both subcategories + products
→ Show subcategories first
→ Then show products

CASE 4:
Category empty
→ Show empty message

